    {
      "lineNumber": 260152,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "最近の状勢を見ると何か大きな変化があったと思われる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Looking at the recent situation, it seems there has been some major change."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260153,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "神がいなくなったりしているのだろ。それに勇者もルール通りに承継されずに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Gods have disappeared or something. Also, the hero didn’t succeed according to the rules."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260154,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あのアホがゾンビになっていたそうだしな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I heard that idiot has become a zombie."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260155,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王も何か変化があるだろう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There must be some changes with the Demon King as well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260156,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "もしかしたらある日、突然　魔王でなくなるかもしれないぞ、がはは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Maybe one day, suddenly, he might stop being the Demon King, haha!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260157,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いや、それはあまりにも楽観視しすぎだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, that’s way too optimistic."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260158,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だが、それくらい前向きに行動していく方がよいとホーネットとか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But Hornet and others say it’s better to act with that much positivity."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260159,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "誰かが学者に報告、ランスへの報告ではない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Someone reported to the scholars, but it was not a report to Rance."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260160,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　大怪獣クエルプランがヘルマン南部に現た",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A giant monster Quelplan appeared in the southern part of Herman."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260161,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そうか、一応監視を続けるように",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I see. Be sure to continue monitoring it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260162,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それをちらっと聞いていたランスは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance, who overheard that a bit,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260163,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "まて、暇だから退治する事にするぞ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Wait, I’m bored so I’ll go and exterminate it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260164,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260165,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "誰かが言う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Someone says,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260166,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それは必要ない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That’s unnecessary."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260167,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大怪獣クエルプランは、すぐに消えます。放置で問題無い",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The giant monster Quelplan will disappear soon. Leaving it alone is no problem."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260168,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そしてとんでもなく危険な存在です。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And it’s an extremely dangerous existence."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260169,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "暴走した神と言われて居ます。魔王様でも危険です。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It is said to be a rampaging god. Even the Demon King is in danger."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260170,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "リセットも補足",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Reset also added,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260171,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　自分達も飲み込まれて危ない目に会いました",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We ourselves were swallowed and faced danger."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260172,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　みんな吸収されて消滅してしまう所でした",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Everyone was about to be absorbed and disappear."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260173,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ダークランス兄さんが長年かけて育てた宝剣グラムも吸収されたし",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The treasured sword Gram, which Dark Rance brother nurtured for many years, was also absorbed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260174,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私達もいくつかの力を失いました",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "We also lost some of our powers."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260175,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "とにかく、せっかくランスが元に戻ったのだし、シィルさんも一緒なんだし",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anyway, since Rance has finally returned and Shial is with him,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260176,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あぶない事をわざわざする必要はないと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "There’s no need to do dangerous things intentionally."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260177,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260178,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いーや、俺様は魔王だ。この世界の支配者だ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Nope, I am the Demon King. I am the ruler of this world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260179,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "神も俺様を恐れていなくなったのに違いない",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The gods must have disappeared out of fear of me."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260180,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "全知全能の存在が俺様なのだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I am the omniscient and omnipotent being."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260181,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そしてこの世界で唯一、好き勝手傍若無人をしても許されるのが俺様だ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And I alone am allowed to behave arbitrarily and arrogantly in this world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260182,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "犯すも奪うも殺すも俺だけの権利だ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To violate, steal, and kill are my exclusive rights."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260183,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "よって、勝手にあばれまわる大怪獣クエルプランは退治だー",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Therefore, I’ll exterminate the giant monster Quelplan that’s rampaging on its own!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260184,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "今からいくぞ、シィルそしてガキどもついてこい！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’m going now! Shial, and kids, come with me!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260185,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "背景　ヘルマン",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Background: Herman"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260186,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスとその子供達はヘルマンに到着した",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and his children arrived at Herman."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260187,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "で、大怪獣はどこだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So, where’s the giant monster?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260188,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ダークランスが一人、じっと１カ所を見ている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Dark Rance is standing alone, staring intently at one spot."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260189,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "見つけたのか",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Have you found it?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260190,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いや、あれは・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, that is..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260191,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260192,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "現れたのは　ネプラカス爺体",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The one who appeared was Grandpa Neplax."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260193,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ダークランスに対して怨みを持っている",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He harbors resentment against Dark Rance."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260194,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "何度も何度も邪魔をしてくれたな、ハーフの分際で、悪魔の裏切り者め",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You kept interfering over and over, for a half-breed, you devil's traitor."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260195,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "だが、自慢の宝剣グラムもクエルプランに吸われ弱体化したな",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But even your prized treasure sword Gram was absorbed by Quelplan and weakened."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260196,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "今日こそは殺してやるぞ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Today, I’ll kill you for sure."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260197,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス「ん、なんだ、この爺、知り合いか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance: 'Hmm, who is this old man? Do I know him?'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260198,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ダークランス「第１階級魔神ネプラカス、悪魔による世界征服をたくらむ奴だ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Dark Rance: 'First class demon god Neplax, a fellow scheming to conquer the world through demons.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260199,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス「ほう、ここにも俺様の世界を侵食しようとするバカがいるのか、蹴散らしてくれる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance: 'Oh, so there’s an idiot here trying to invade my world. I’ll scatter him.'"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260200,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "な、魔王ランスだと・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "W-wait, it’s Demon King Rance..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260201,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "＞戦闘",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ">Battle"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260202,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ちっ・・どこかに消えやがったか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Tch... Has it disappeared somewhere?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260203,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "かなり傷を与えたから、しばらくはでてこないだろう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I dealt considerable damage, so it probably won’t show up for a while."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260204,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ネプラカスを撃破した",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Neplax has been defeated."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260205,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260206,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（ＣＧ：クエルプラン遭遇）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(CG: Encounter with Quelplan)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260207,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "さて、あれが大怪獣クエルプランだな。うむ、でかいな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Now then, that is the giant monster Quelplan. Hmm, it’s huge."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260208,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ん・・クエルプラン・・んんん、どこかで聞いた事のある名だな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hmm... Quelplan... hmmm, that’s a name I’ve heard somewhere."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260209,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "それはそうでしょ、世界最大の厄災として有名な大怪獣ですから",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That’s right, it’s a giant monster famous as the greatest calamity in the world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260210,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いや、そうじゃなくて、もっと前に・・俺が人間だった頃・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, not that. Earlier... back when I was human..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260211,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "・・・",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "..."
    }
  ]
}

